    Working since 15 Sep 2007
Comments:
    Implementation test for strict hyperviscosity. One can either check that
    the derivatives at all scales are as expected, using idl/hypvistest.pro, or
    run the the simulation to check for momentum conservation.
References:
    ``Inertial range scaling in numerical turbulence with hyperviscosity''
    Haugen N.E., & Brandenburg A. 2004
    PRE, vol. 70, p. 26405-
